Test Matrix:
------------
1. Sensitivity Tests
   - Minimum detectable field (nT/√Hz)
   - Spatial resolution (μm)
   - Temporal resolution (ms)

2. Range Tests
   - Maximum detection range
   - Range vs. object size
   - Atmospheric effects

3. Multi-Target Tests
   - Object separation resolution
   - Simultaneous tracking capacity
   - Cross-talk between sensors

4. Environmental Robustness
   - Temperature stability
   - Vibration immunity
   - EMI rejection

5. Quantum Advantage Verification
   - Compare with classical baseline
   - Entanglement verification
   - Non-classical correlation measurement
